<p><a name="History_of_ideas" id="History_of_ideas"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Conservation_of_energy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: History of ideas">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">History of ideas</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBrown.2C_T.M.1965">Brown, T.M. (1965). "Resource letter EEC-1 on the evolution of energy concepts from Galileo to Helmholtz". <i>American Journal of Physics</i> <b>33</b>: 759–765. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1119%2F1.1970980" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1119%2F1.1970980" rel="nofollow">10.1119/1.1970980</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Resource+letter+EEC-1+on+the+evolution+of+energy+concepts+from+Galileo+to+Helmholtz&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Journal+of+Physics&amp;rft.aulast=Brown%2C+T.M.&amp;rft.au=Brown%2C+T.M.&amp;rft.date=1965&amp;rft.volume=33&amp;rft.pages=759%E2%80%93765&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1119%2F1.1970980&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Conservation_of_energy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
